    <section class="tool-explainer">
      <h2>How to use the Tip Calculator</h2>
      <p>Enter your total bill amount, select a tip percentage (15%, 18%, 20%, or a custom amount), and specify how many people are splitting the bill. The calculator instantly shows the tip amount and the total each person owes.</p>

      <h2>How tip is calculated</h2>
      <p>Tip amount = Bill total &times; (Tip % &divide; 100). Per-person share = (Bill total + Tip amount) &divide; Number of people. For example, a $80 bill with an 18% tip among 4 people: tip = $14.40, total = $94.40, per person = $23.60.</p>

